<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>

<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
              android:id="@+id/dialog_event_brainfuzz"
              android:orientation="vertical"
              android:padding="5dp"
              android:layout_width="match_parent"
              android:layout_height="match_parent">

    <ImageView
            android:layout_width="fill_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/imageView"
            android:src="@drawable/event_brainfuzz"/>

    <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceLarge"
            android:text="About"
            android:id="@+id/aboutTitleBrainfuzz"
            android:layout_gravity="left|center_vertical"/>

    <TextView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="“First, solve the problem. Then, write the code.” – John Johnson \n
GET READY TO SCRATCH YOUR HEAD..!!! BRAINFUZZ IS BACK..!! \n
This is a event in which you all have to fuzz your brains ( ie write algorithms ) on the questions presented and only psuedocodes are required. Get ready to solve challenging problems and showcase your talents.
For in the end LOGIC IS MIGHT ! Aside from teams lone wolves are also allowed."
            android:layout_gravity="center"/>


</LinearLayout>